kedaop.name: kedaop
values:
image:
  keda:
    repository: ghcr.io/kedacore/keda
    tag: ""
  metricsApiServer:
    repository: ghcr.io/kedacore/keda-metrics-apiserver

    repository: ghcr.io/kedacore/keda-admission-webhooks

    initialDelaySeconds: 25

    failureThreshold: 3
    successThreshold: 1
  readinessProbe:
    initialDelaySeconds: 20
    periodSeconds: 3
    timeoutSeconds: 1

    successThreshold: 1
metricsServer:

    successThreshold: 1
  readinessProbe:
    initialDelaySeconds: 5
    periodSeconds: 3
    timeoutSeconds: 1
    failureThreshold: 3
    successThreshold: 1

  port: 9443
